snippet.title: Dream Cage - Official Reveal Trailer
snippet.description: Get your first look at Dream Cage, a new horror game inspired by the V/H/S films that puts you in the shoes of a 50-year-old insomniac struggling with sleep paralysis who must grapple with his fears realized before his eyes over five terrifying nights. Wishlist it on Steam if you're interested: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3122170/Dream_Cage
